  <brief_title>Randomized Controlled Trial of Subcuticular Skin Closure Versus Steri-strip S Closure</brief_title>
  <official_title>Closing Linear Incisions in Plastic Surgery: A Randomized Clinical Trial Comparing a New Coaptive Film Device Versus Standard Subcuticular Sutures for Scar Quality, Patient Comfort, and Closure Time</official_title>
  <sponsors>
